display_long_description:
Dive into a Mixed Reality adventure with “MR Fish”!
Experience the thrill of fishing like never before as your room transforms into a lively underwater environment. Designed for Meta Quest 3, “MR Fish” uses hand tracking and spatial awareness to let you interact with fish that swim around your real-world space.
Walk, dodge, and reach out to grab fish of all shapes and sizes as they dart through your living room. The gameplay is simple to learn but rewarding to master, making it ideal for both casual players and families. With stunning visuals, realistic fish behavior, and light physical activity, this MR game is perfect for parties, education, or just a relaxing escape from reality.
Key Features:

Mixed Reality fishing in your real space

Hand-tracking and intuitive gestures

Colorful fish and varied environments

Safe, active fun for all ages

Get ready to catch more than just fish — catch unforgettable moments!
